{
  "texts": [
    "For obtaining the real-time pose estimation, hand pose, and facial expression the authors used Kinect RGB-D camera.",
    "In addition, Zhang et al. [29] proposed a new method for pose estimation using a Kinect sensor with a perspective n-points (PnP) algorithm.",
    "The proposed PnP algorithm is used to get the relative position of various cameras and to map real 3D points of space with the 2D camera image.",
    "Sarsfield et al. [30] introduced a clinical assessment of human posture using a Kinect sensor.",
    "The authors performed a comprehensive analysis for pose estimation in rehabilitation applications."
  ]
}